Class AbstractRepository<T>

java.lang.Object
repository.AbstractRepository<T>
Type Parameters:
T - Object type
Direct Known Subclasses:
GenericRepository
public abstract class AbstractRepository<T> extends Object
Enforces an abstract interface for the template class to implement. Methods here should only be internally called
